{"tid":1928622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔通老細買左假口罩比我地用？！我唔想中肺炎啊！","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T00:03:49.000Z","uid":310655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f29c9db2fb37930080806c52cd7fdf9a1d7507","tid":1928622,"uid":310655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"向口罩高手求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老細之前托佢朋友係美國訂左一批口罩番香港，最近比左十盒我地同事係公司用，但我地見到個包裝果下真係崩潰，咪就係傳說中既假口罩！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/16/182823_83d13af461eaf4e91830a65648be3f35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F16%2F182823_83d13af461eaf4e91830a65648be3f35.png&h=27cb7f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM0z1jz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM0z1jz.png&h=a1b4ff40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unUALMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunUALMv.png&h=c080c75a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDu5oyu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDu5oyu.png&h=5fffb1f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLaHqMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLaHqMY.jpg&h=f341d637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右：老細口罩，左：私人真口罩<br />\n<br />\n呢個口罩無論摸上手定戴上面，都只可以話佢一個字：薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然感覺好過民賤聯派果啲，但事關我地係做醫療既，日日對住唔同既病人，口罩真係好重要！有冇人可以話比我知呢盒口罩係真定假，因為上網真係搵唔到咩資料，我地暫時搵到既資料係Pro-Safe呢個品牌係黎自一間係New York，叫MSC既公司，但佢個官網係上唔到，開左VPN都上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇怪既點係，佢其他product個商標都係用圓圈R（即係已註冊商標），但老細呢盒口罩係用TM，係咪代表佢係假口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxJazFs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxJazFs.jpg&h=b40fa9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpmjs0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqpmjs0t.jpg&h=87f95816&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0fdd7146727f9207802167ebf91c4bae96208c","tid":1928622,"uid":310655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9611bc6c60c0bbfa4309cf5c61ac28bb32b97b7e","tid":1928622,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}